description: [``botocore``] Added QSearchBar option for GenerateEmbedUrlForRegisteredUser ExperienceConfiguration to support Q search bar embedding

[``botocore``] This release introduces character restrictions for ControlSet names. We updated regex patterns for the following attributes: ControlSet, CreateAssessmentFrameworkControlSet, and UpdateAssessmentFrameworkControlSet.
[``botocore``] Chime VoiceConnector and VoiceConnectorGroup APIs will now return an ARN.
